{
  "stem": "23645.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was sort of the same barracks, you know, that I've described.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, again, the Russians were advancing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we got taken out of Czestochowa, packed into cattle trains.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that was a horrible trip.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] The-- the hunger and-- and the cold, and-- it was just, just awful.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Some--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Just a jacket, [BACKROUND NOISE] with a pair of pants.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were long pants that were up to here, you know, and I had a rope tied around, because they weren't my own clothes anymore.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I had lost them in-- in one of the showers that I went through.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's also another story.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't know if you want me to say that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My father had put pictures and some jewelry in-- in the lining of-- of my jacket.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And those-- you know, that was my sort of security.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And when we were put through the showers, you undress, and you go through the showers-- At that time, we already knew about some of the showers being disguised as, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] you know-- uh-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] as a-- not-- not a crematorium, the, uh-- the gas chamber.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They were disguised, these gas chambers, you know, because they didn't want any panic.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So, with this knowledge, suddenly we're in this huge shower--",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was when we got-- there was one in Czestochowa, but there's also one in Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was extremely big.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were suspicious.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I remember, all-- we were there-- the first time that I lost my clothes was in Czestochowa.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So-- piece of soap, naked, with a whole bunch of people here, and we wait.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And finally we see the water come down and not-- not the gas, and we-- ah!",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We're going to live!",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We're going to live.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
